articles.title: I Tried These Two TikTok Painting Hacks, and I willl Never Go Back to The Way I Used to Pour Paint Again
articles.body: I recently painted a wall in my living room (aka, my office, coffee area, and gym). I love how it turned out. What I did not love? How freaking impossible it was to pour paint from the can to the tray without making a mess.
